text: I recently completed a Python bootcamp and can attest to the effectiveness of the course. My toe surgery recovery has been smooth sailing since then, with no sensitivity issues whatsoever. For those starting their coding journey, I'd recommend considering both "100 Days of Code" and "Python Pro Bootcamp by Dr. Angela Yu." Other notable options include IBM Python for Data Science, Google Crash Course on Python, and various University of Michigan courses. Happy coding!
